    <section id="sect-00002">
    <title>Calling a function</title>
    <para id="para-00002">Throughout the book, functions have been called to perform tasks. Ex: print() prints values, and sqrt() calculates the square root. A <term id="term-00001">function</term> is a named, reusable block of code that performs a task when called.</para>
