    <note class="practice-program" id="note-00007">
    <title>Cinema concession stand</title>
    <para id="para-00015">Write a function, concessions(), that prints the food and drink options at a cinema.</para>
    <para id="para-00016">Given:</para>
    <code class="python" lang="python">
    concessions()
    </code>
    <para id="para-00017">The output is:</para>
    <code class="python" lang="python">
    Food/Drink Options:
    Popcorn: $8-10
    Candy: $3-5
    Soft drink: $5-7
    </code>
